00:07:54,010 --> 00:07:57,010
我一共才卖了两盒 还被偷了一盒
<i>I had sold two boxes of cookies and had one stolen.</i>

183
00:07:57,339 --> 00:07:58,890
我得想个新点子
<i>I needed a new strategy.</i>

184
00:07:59,134 --> 00:08:01,506
打扰下 想来盒饼干吗?
Excuse me. would you like to buy a box of cookies?

185
00:08:01,588 --> 00:08:03,630
它们能喝吗?
Can I get drunk on those cookies?

186
00:08:08,845 --> 00:08:10,703
嗨 Risky 想来盒饼干吗?
Hey, Risky, you want to buy a box of cookies?

187
00:08:10,704 --> 00:08:12,880
嘿 小朋友 俺管卖不管买
Hey, youngblood, I don't buy, I sell.

188
00:08:12,929 --> 00:08:14,210
想来个VCR吗?
You want to buy a VCR?

189
00:08:14,211 --> 00:08:15,211
不 谢谢
No, thanks.

190
00:08:15,429 --> 00:08:17,079
嘿 要买VCR吗?
Hey. You need a VCR?

191
00:08:17,224 --> 00:08:18,282
我已经有一个了
I got one already.

192
00:08:18,324 --> 00:08:19,656
这可是今早从卡车上掉下来的
Fell off the truck this morning.

193
00:08:19,691 --> 00:08:21,377
真的吗? 我来两个
Really? I'll take two.

194
00:08:21,476 --> 00:08:24,536
真没想到这街区唯一能卖出去的
<i>I never realized the only stuff that sold on the street</i>

195
00:08:24,537 --> 00:08:26,654
竟是偷来的东西
<i>in my neighborhood was stolen stuff.</i>

196
00:08:27,038 --> 00:08:29,070
饼干!  卖饼干!
Cookies!  Cookies for sale!

197
00:08:29,139 --> 00:08:32,068
巧克力曲奇 花生酱口味 巧克力人偶 薄荷巧克力口味
Chocolate chip, peanut butter, Do-Si-Do, chocolate mint!

198
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,200
