I got cookies.

199
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:36,070
这可是今早从卡车上掉下来的
They just fell off the truck this morning.

200
00:08:37,255 --> 00:08:38,700
你怎么不早说?
Why didn't you say so?

201
00:08:39,354 --> 00:08:40,412
我要两盒
Give me two boxes.

202
00:08:53,581 --> 00:08:54,720
